---
title: BBQ Veggie Mince Loaded Wedges with Tomato Salsa & Plant-Based Aioli
description: Prepare for a table full of happy faces when you bring out this crowd-pleasing dish. With herby potato wedges, gently spiced
veggie mince, tomato-charred corn salsa and a dollop of plant-based aioli, it's going all the way to number one!
